title: Announcement date of the First Half 2015 Financial Results (Piraeus Bank SA)
text: (Source: Piraeus Bank SA) Piraeus Bank would like to inform the investment community that the Announcement of the Group's First Half 2015 Financial Results will take place on Wednesday, 14 October 2015, post ATHEX trading session closing. Athens, Monday 12 October, 2015 distributed by This content was issued by Piraeus Bank SA on the 2015-10-12 and was initially posted on www.piraeusbank.gr. It was distributed, unedited and unaltered, by noodls on 2015-10-12 13:13:13 UTC. The original issuer is solely responsible for the accuracy of the information contained therein. (noodl: 30283158)
